examples.why_selected:
Combines
  data portability (Art. 20) and right to erasure (Art. 17) in one place;
  provides granular export format choices.

examples.title:
Mandatory
  DOB on sign‑up; accounts under 13 diverted to “TikTok for Younger Users”;
  Family Pairing lets parents link and manage screen‑time, DMs, content.

Info icon
  opens overlay describing listening habits, liked songs influencing mix;
  dismissible tip.

Web
  account dashboard lists enrolled palms with “Delete” and confirmation dialog;
  email confirmation follows.

Browser
  banner requests “Immersive VR” & “CAMERA” permissions separately;
  highlight warns about surrounding capture.
